data.title: Wiggins Man Sentenced To Prison For Possession with Intent to Distribute over 250 Grams of a Substance Containing Fentanyl
data.meta_description: A Wiggins man was sentenced to 84 months in federal prison for possession with intent to distribute over 250 grams of a substance containing fentanyl.
